  <name>Tetzle</name>
  <summary>Jigsaw puzzle with tetromino pieces</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Tetzle is a jigsaw puzzle game that uses tetrominoes for the pieces. Any image can be imported and used to create puzzles with a wide range of sizes. Games are saved automatically, and you can select between currently in progress games.</p>
  </description>

